ygData.messageBody:
Hail, Brothers and Sisters of the Shadow

My name is Envy, and I'm new on the discussion list. As a dark elf SK on
the Tunare Server, I'm in Neriak right now, but soon I'll be spreading
my chaos to Qeynos. I also have a necromancer "companion" named Darque.
Just wanted to introduce myself, and say hello to everyone, >;-)
--"hello everyone!"

As for the SK casting dispute, I think it has to do with your skills'
levels.

See you online...

Envy,
La Comtesse de Obscuritï¿½
